OL,3,CBBC to cut 2,000 jobs as organisation
OL,4,Ctries to reduce costs
OL,6,FThe BBC will cut 2,000 jobs as it
OL,7,Ftries to reduce costs by 10% over the
OL,8,Fnext three years.
OL,10,FThe cuts mark the biggest round of BBC
OL,11,Fredundancies in almost 15 years.
OL,13,FIt comes as former Google boss Matt
OL,14,FBrittin is set to take over as the
OL,15,FBBC's director-general on May 18.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
