OL,3,CBBC to cut 2,000 jobs as organisation
OL,4,Ctries to reduce costs
OL,6,FThe organisation previously announced
OL,7,Faround 450 job losses in 2020, with
OL,8,Fcuts to Newsnight, 5Live and other
OL,9,Fnews output, as the corporation said
OL,10,Fit wanted to "reduce duplication"
OL,11,Fwhile making savings of #80 million.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
