OL,3,CBBC to cut 2,000 jobs as organisation
OL,4,Ctries to reduce costs
OL,6,FThe BBC has previously said: "Over the
OL,7,Flast three years we have delivered
OL,8,Fmore than a half a billion pounds
OL,9,Fworth of savings, much of which we've
OL,10,Fbeen able to reinvest into our output
OL,11,Facross the BBC.
OL,13,F"In a rapidly changing media market,
OL,14,Fwe continue to face substantial
OL,15,Ffinancial pressures. As a result we
OL,16,Fexpect to make further savings over
OL,17,Fthe next three years of around 10% of
OL,18,Four costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
