OL,3,CBBC to cut 2,000 jobs as organisation
OL,4,Ctries to reduce costs
OL,6,F"This is about the BBC becoming more
OL,7,Fproductive and prioritising our offer
OL,8,Fto audiences to ensure we're providing
OL,9,Fthe best value for money, both now and
OL,10,Fin the future."
